WEBVTT

01:35.700 --> 01:39.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:39.980 --> 01:42.980
[Episode 23]

02:02.120 --> 02:02.650
Bai Ze.

02:03.710 --> 02:04.410
What was that?

02:08.510 --> 02:09.260
Ji Can, a Lonescale.

02:10.200 --> 02:10.980
Ji Can?

02:12.400 --> 02:13.420
Unlike your name,

02:14.030 --> 02:14.690
"ji" here

02:15.520 --> 02:16.650
refers to loneliness.

02:19.000 --> 02:20.740
Do you feel lonely right now?

02:24.120 --> 02:24.970
Not just now.

02:27.310 --> 02:28.340
It's always been this way.

02:30.190 --> 02:31.180
Chi Wen's dragon scale,

02:31.180 --> 02:32.340
which you once swallowed,

02:32.840 --> 02:34.020
has been inside you,

02:35.750 --> 02:37.300
feeding on your loneliness

02:37.750 --> 02:38.860
all this time.

02:39.470 --> 02:40.810
Finally, it took form,

02:41.400 --> 02:42.300
becoming a demon.

02:43.400 --> 02:44.620
A demon named Lonescale.

02:46.630 --> 02:47.530
Over the years,

02:48.430 --> 02:49.370
you held high positions

02:49.430 --> 02:50.420
as the Dragon Deity,

02:51.190 --> 02:52.210
beloved by everyone.

02:53.400 --> 02:54.630
But no one really understands

02:54.630 --> 02:55.770
your loneliness.

03:00.750 --> 03:02.210
You stay alone in the Scale Cave,

03:03.750 --> 03:04.770
accompanied

03:06.120 --> 03:07.140
only by your shadow.

03:08.710 --> 03:09.860
Over the years,

03:11.680 --> 03:13.620
your loneliness gave birth to this demon.

03:14.680 --> 03:16.210
It embodies the untold loneliness

03:16.710 --> 03:18.140
deep in your heart.

03:21.150 --> 03:22.180
Throughout the ages,

03:24.120 --> 03:25.740
there have been only two Lonescales.

03:27.120 --> 03:28.650
Because only the loneliest beings

03:29.360 --> 03:31.020
can give birth to this demon.

03:33.870 --> 03:34.580
Two?

03:37.630 --> 03:38.530
Where's the other one?

03:50.560 --> 03:51.460
Do you remember?

03:52.470 --> 03:53.690
Lu Wuyi keeps saying

03:54.190 --> 03:56.140
that you carry a unique fragrance.

03:56.870 --> 03:57.740
Master Dragon Deity.

03:59.960 --> 04:01.900
You have such a special fragrance.

04:03.470 --> 04:05.460
I've never smelled it in the mortal world.

04:06.150 --> 04:07.340
How come

04:08.630 --> 04:10.530
you've obtained a fragrance?

04:12.590 --> 04:13.530
Is it because of him?

04:14.430 --> 04:15.210
Dragon bone,

04:15.590 --> 04:16.340
dragon saliva,

04:16.910 --> 04:18.020
dragon blood, and dragon scale

04:18.430 --> 04:19.370
all carry a fragrance.

04:20.190 --> 04:21.570
Lonescale is essentially a dragon scale

04:22.000 --> 04:23.250
feeding on your loneliness.

04:24.160 --> 04:24.740
Therefore,

04:25.160 --> 04:27.010
it also carries a unique scent.

04:27.800 --> 04:29.300
But this scent

04:30.600 --> 04:32.420
makes people sad,

04:34.070 --> 04:36.740
as if they're hollowed out.

04:38.160 --> 04:39.570
But this fragrance

04:41.360 --> 04:43.060
leaves a hollow ache in the heart,

04:43.390 --> 04:46.300
like a valley full of blooming flowers,

04:46.480 --> 04:48.220
yet utterly devoid of people.

04:48.430 --> 04:49.740
It's like flowers in an empty valley

04:50.310 --> 04:51.450
or thick snow on an ancient temple.

04:52.240 --> 04:53.490
The lonelier you are inside,

04:53.750 --> 04:55.130
the stronger this scent becomes.

04:56.390 --> 04:58.330
Master Dragon Deity, your fragrance

04:59.000 --> 04:59.980
seems to be lighter.

05:01.000 --> 05:03.130
Why is your fragrance fading?

05:03.680 --> 05:04.420
Nonsense.

05:09.190 --> 05:11.420
Then why can't anyone smell it,

05:12.870 --> 05:14.060
including me?

05:14.720 --> 05:15.660
Only those

05:15.660 --> 05:16.980
who truly understand your loneliness

05:18.560 --> 05:19.540
can smell it.

05:23.630 --> 05:24.570
It's true.

05:24.950 --> 05:26.300
I'm not lying to you.

05:29.680 --> 05:30.930
As we approach the end,

05:31.040 --> 05:32.010
things get more unpredictable,

05:32.750 --> 05:34.540
and you grow more hesitant

05:34.800 --> 05:35.420
and hurt.

05:36.800 --> 05:37.420
Right?

05:40.950 --> 05:42.060
I'm not hesitant.

05:43.870 --> 05:44.740
I'm afraid.

05:46.950 --> 05:47.780
I'm scared

05:48.600 --> 05:50.100
that after so many years of struggle,

05:52.070 --> 05:54.370
I'd fail to live up to your expectations

05:56.680 --> 05:57.930
and let you down

05:59.830 --> 06:00.740
in the end.

06:02.190 --> 06:03.570
But you're also scared to succeed.

06:05.070 --> 06:05.570
Aren't you?

06:06.870 --> 06:08.420
Because to reach the end,

06:08.720 --> 06:09.690
you must accept

06:09.750 --> 06:11.010
the fact that you'd lose her.

06:14.070 --> 06:15.780
That's why I cherish

06:15.870 --> 06:17.420
every moment I have with her.

06:18.830 --> 06:20.620
Why are you torturing yourself?

06:20.800 --> 06:21.890
I don't want to lose her.

06:24.390 --> 06:25.490
But it's inevitable.

06:30.000 --> 06:30.930
I have no choice.

06:33.160 --> 06:34.860
But you have to make a choice.

06:36.750 --> 06:37.800
Or you'll be devoured

06:37.800 --> 06:38.810
by Lonescale.

06:40.390 --> 06:41.540
What will happen

06:45.560 --> 06:46.660
if I am devoured?

06:50.680 --> 06:51.370
Master Dragon Deity.

07:01.160 --> 07:01.860
Master Bai Ze.

07:02.600 --> 07:03.490
What brought you here?

07:06.190 --> 07:07.100
How's everything going?

07:08.120 --> 07:08.980
The Spirit-Binding Ring

07:09.680 --> 07:10.980
and the Dragon Deity's Power of Han Ba

07:11.720 --> 07:12.980
were snatched away by Lu Wuyi.

07:16.160 --> 07:17.660
What exactly does she want?

07:18.750 --> 07:19.420
No idea.

07:20.720 --> 07:21.930
She simply vanished.

07:23.430 --> 07:24.980
The Dragon Deity's Power is crucial.

07:25.750 --> 07:26.780
We must find her.

07:31.480 --> 07:33.690
Master, why did your fragrance

07:34.600 --> 07:36.010
suddenly grow so intense?

07:38.750 --> 07:40.010
You also smell it, Commander Li?

07:41.870 --> 07:43.660
I don't think you could smell it before.

07:45.040 --> 07:45.660
That's right.

07:46.830 --> 07:48.540
Lu Wuyi kept mentioning it,

07:50.560 --> 07:51.490
and I've been curious.

07:52.310 --> 07:53.130
I didn't expect

07:54.000 --> 07:55.100
this fragrance

07:55.510 --> 07:57.220
to be so heartbreaking.

07:59.160 --> 07:59.930
It feels like

08:02.240 --> 08:03.540
entering an ancient temple

08:04.240 --> 08:06.250
abandoned in the heavy snow.

08:52.670 --> 08:53.500
I know him.

08:54.150 --> 08:55.450
I've seen him at the Dragon Deity Temple.

08:55.910 --> 08:56.930
He's Master Chi Wen.

08:57.510 --> 08:58.900
The Dragon Deity really descended.

08:59.240 --> 09:00.690
We're saved.

09:01.810 --> 09:02.630
Yes!

09:02.630 --> 09:03.380
Master Chi Wen.

09:04.400 --> 09:05.490
Help us.

09:10.050 --> 09:11.330
Master Chi Wen.

09:12.780 --> 09:14.200
Master Chi Wen.

09:21.080 --> 09:21.810
I know him.

09:22.030 --> 09:23.180
He's Master Chi Wen.

09:23.270 --> 09:24.540
I've seen him at the Dragon Deity Temple.

09:24.750 --> 09:25.420
Master Chi Wen.

09:25.670 --> 09:26.260
Master Chi Wen.

09:26.480 --> 09:27.140
Master Chi Wen.

09:27.200 --> 09:28.540
Please bestow rainfall upon us.

09:28.550 --> 09:29.540
Please help us.

09:29.790 --> 09:30.540
Master Chi Wen.

09:30.870 --> 09:32.140
Please help us.

09:32.270 --> 09:33.540
Please help us.

09:34.670 --> 09:35.730
He is not a Dragon Deity.

09:35.910 --> 09:37.180
He can't help us at all.

09:37.320 --> 09:38.000
We've been worshipping

09:38.000 --> 09:38.780
and admiring him,

09:38.870 --> 09:39.850
but he doesn't do anything.

09:40.000 --> 09:41.610
- Get him. - Get him.

10:11.510 --> 10:12.120
Where's Master Dragon Deity?

10:12.120 --> 10:13.180
- Where is he? - Where did he go?

10:13.690 --> 10:14.640
- He's gone. - Master is gone.

10:15.600 --> 10:16.380
Where did he go?

10:16.790 --> 10:17.560
Where's Master Dragon Deity?

10:31.440 --> 10:32.450
What Ji Ling said is true.

10:33.270 --> 10:34.610
Lu Wuyi deceived us.

10:36.030 --> 10:36.780
You weren't the one

10:36.780 --> 10:38.490
who cast the Word Magic on Mu Long.

10:39.150 --> 10:39.970
It was my sister.

10:41.360 --> 10:41.850
Ji Ling.

10:42.550 --> 10:43.260
I'm sorry.

10:46.120 --> 10:47.090
My name is Mu Long.

10:47.790 --> 10:49.420
My mother named me Mu Long,

10:49.960 --> 10:51.450
which means "admiring dragons."

10:53.120 --> 10:54.140
Our entire family

10:54.750 --> 10:56.020
sees Master Dragon Deity

10:56.200 --> 10:57.730
as an almighty...

10:58.000 --> 10:59.500
They all believed in him.

11:00.000 --> 11:01.420
But I never did.

11:02.390 --> 11:03.330
Because I thought

11:04.320 --> 11:05.540
if there were dragons

11:05.960 --> 11:06.850
in this world

11:07.390 --> 11:08.730
that could eliminate disaster,

11:09.360 --> 11:11.380
then no creature would be suffering.

11:12.320 --> 11:13.260
So I didn't believe in him.

11:14.000 --> 11:14.900
Nor did I worship him.

11:15.750 --> 11:17.690
Therefore, I hated my name.

11:19.320 --> 11:21.060
Is Master Dragon Deity aware

11:21.870 --> 11:23.610
of all the worldly suffering?

11:42.510 --> 11:43.450
But then,

11:44.390 --> 11:46.690
my great-grandmother fell ill after a stroke.

11:47.120 --> 11:48.380
I had no choice.

11:49.030 --> 11:49.450
I...

11:49.750 --> 11:50.060
I...

11:50.080 --> 11:51.210
I had to worship

11:51.240 --> 11:52.450
and beg him.

11:53.150 --> 11:54.780
At that moment, I finally realized

11:54.790 --> 11:56.060
what he tried to show us.

11:56.720 --> 11:58.330
What sustains us through suffering

11:59.120 --> 12:00.090
and helps us defeat evil...

12:00.360 --> 12:01.970
is not the blessing of the deities

12:02.960 --> 12:04.610
but the hope we have.

12:06.600 --> 12:07.570
Here you are.

12:11.480 --> 12:13.020
Lu Wuyi will come.

12:15.120 --> 12:16.660
I have to stop her.

12:17.200 --> 12:18.140
Lu Wuyi will come?

12:19.150 --> 12:19.690
Yes.

12:21.480 --> 12:22.210
I dreamed of it.

12:24.870 --> 12:25.570
And

12:27.720 --> 12:28.660
I was here too.

12:29.080 --> 12:29.930
No.

12:30.840 --> 12:31.690
No.

12:32.750 --> 12:33.450
Ji Ling.

12:33.750 --> 12:34.300
Dream?

12:35.390 --> 12:36.540
Like Ji Ling,

12:36.960 --> 12:38.330
I've also had a similar dream.

12:40.910 --> 12:41.610
In that dream,

12:42.480 --> 12:44.180
you were possessed by Jiu Ying

12:45.360 --> 12:46.850
after gathering all the Dragon Deity's Power.

12:47.120 --> 12:48.500
Jiu Ying manipulated you

12:48.550 --> 12:49.500
to kill Chi Wen.

12:50.320 --> 12:51.930
So Ji Ling is not trustworthy.

12:55.150 --> 12:55.840
But I've also

12:55.840 --> 12:56.840
seen him

12:56.840 --> 12:57.610
in Chi Wen's memory.

12:58.390 --> 12:59.690
His eyes were crystal clear,

13:00.510 --> 13:01.330
free from all impurity.

13:02.120 --> 13:03.500
I'm reluctant to believe

13:04.320 --> 13:05.810
that he covets the dragon throne.

13:07.200 --> 13:07.850
Otherwise,

13:09.000 --> 13:09.750
there wouldn't be

13:09.750 --> 13:11.500
so many outstanding double-flower hunters

13:11.510 --> 13:12.730
who vow to follow him.

13:13.910 --> 13:15.020
This moment

13:15.390 --> 13:17.450
has been repeated countless times.

13:18.910 --> 13:19.850
All of us

13:20.720 --> 13:22.690
have been going back in time over and over.

13:24.200 --> 13:25.140
Those are not dreams,

13:25.750 --> 13:27.660
but what really happened.

13:29.150 --> 13:30.930
It was repeated too many times

13:33.270 --> 13:35.180
and was etched in the depths of our consciousness

13:37.630 --> 13:38.970
like a vague dream.

13:39.580 --> 13:42.060
♪How pitiful, how sad...♪

13:46.510 --> 13:47.500
Now,

13:50.320 --> 13:51.180
I have finally realized

13:53.200 --> 13:54.780
what exactly Wu wanted to do.

13:55.020 --> 13:57.860
♪To go back and see my hometown...♪

13:58.600 --> 14:00.060
The man she's trying to save

14:01.180 --> 14:03.780
♪As I drift farther away...♪

14:03.790 --> 14:04.850
is not Wu Wangyan.

14:07.720 --> 14:08.660
The years are too long,

14:09.670 --> 14:11.450
long enough to change our original intention.

14:14.320 --> 14:15.420
People change.

14:24.390 --> 14:25.690
Ji Ling can lie to me.

14:27.840 --> 14:28.810
But Lu Wuyi

14:29.510 --> 14:30.420
can also lie to you.

14:32.870 --> 14:34.380
One of them

14:35.720 --> 14:37.210
has to be lying.

14:41.320 --> 14:42.380
Wu lied to me.

14:44.550 --> 14:45.570
I lied to her too.

14:45.820 --> 14:47.820
♪In the cold rain, on the mountain...♪

14:47.840 --> 14:48.730
We are

14:50.150 --> 14:51.210
both lying.

14:52.420 --> 14:56.220
♪Heartbroken people are asleep...♪

14:56.270 --> 14:56.930
Ji.

14:58.440 --> 14:59.540
You lied to me.

15:02.840 --> 15:04.500
You've been lying to me.

15:08.020 --> 15:10.820
♪Sever our tie, stop this resentment♪

15:12.140 --> 15:15.260
♪I stole the spring♪

15:15.620 --> 15:18.500
♪To see the mountain flowers bloom with you♪

15:18.940 --> 15:21.540
♪Drink to our heart's content in the wind♪

15:21.700 --> 15:24.500
♪The skeleton holds up the oath♪

15:25.060 --> 15:28.020
♪But the color of my loneliness♪

15:28.220 --> 15:30.940
♪Resembles the setting sun dyeing the shackles♪

15:34.620 --> 15:37.660
♪Sing lightly, a soft chorus♪

15:38.480 --> 15:39.690
So what are you going to do?

15:48.150 --> 15:49.020
No matter what,

15:52.390 --> 15:54.180
I must retrieve the Dragon Deity's Power.

16:05.910 --> 16:06.450
Stop.

16:12.480 --> 16:13.090
Wu.

16:16.360 --> 16:18.140
Why can she activate the Spirit-Binding Ring?

16:22.840 --> 16:24.330
She has the dragon's scent.

16:27.730 --> 16:28.420
How come?

16:32.510 --> 16:33.300
It's the Lonescale.

16:33.910 --> 16:35.420
She has the sacred power of a Lonescale.

16:36.840 --> 16:38.300
The Lonescale is transformed from dragon scales.

16:39.080 --> 16:40.930
The Spirit-Binding Ring was confused by the scent

16:41.360 --> 16:42.730
and recognized her as its master.

16:43.480 --> 16:44.180
But

16:45.150 --> 16:45.970
why does she

16:46.000 --> 16:47.610
carry the scent of a Lonescale?

17:02.030 --> 17:02.660
Wu.

17:05.840 --> 17:06.810
We are still

17:08.790 --> 17:10.610
in a rewind.

17:12.160 --> 17:12.740
Right?

17:23.920 --> 17:25.890
You've been through

17:29.440 --> 17:30.890
countless rewinds,

17:33.350 --> 17:34.740
enduring all the pain

17:37.200 --> 17:39.090
just to save someone.

18:06.750 --> 18:08.090
The person you've wanted to save

18:13.030 --> 18:14.220
has always been me.

18:18.510 --> 18:19.170
Right?

18:26.830 --> 18:27.940
Deception.

18:30.720 --> 18:32.740
Perhaps only lies and deception

18:35.680 --> 18:37.410
can help me save you.

18:39.200 --> 18:39.810
Ji Ling.

18:40.590 --> 18:41.260
Ji Ling.

18:47.680 --> 18:48.410
Ji Ling.

20:09.680 --> 20:10.170
Yes.

20:19.900 --> 20:24.070
[First time]

20:24.070 --> 20:24.960
I have sent Wu Wangyan's body

20:24.960 --> 20:26.260
back to the Formless Moon.

20:27.110 --> 20:27.880
He will be resurrected

20:27.880 --> 20:29.330
from the Primordial Sacred Spring soon.

20:30.750 --> 20:32.130
And Wu Shiguang

20:32.160 --> 20:33.650
is about to slay the dragon.

20:35.000 --> 20:36.980
I have played this game with you for years.

20:39.200 --> 20:40.460
The game is finally settled.

20:41.830 --> 20:43.740
I've accompanied you on this final journey.

20:45.680 --> 20:47.130
Once this heavy rain falls,

20:49.160 --> 20:49.980
my mission

20:52.030 --> 20:53.020
will be completed.

21:00.590 --> 21:02.650
No one can control three demon powers simultaneously.

21:04.310 --> 21:05.570
Your spiritual veins will be torn,

21:08.720 --> 21:09.810
and your soul shattered.

21:10.270 --> 21:11.300
I've made up my mind.

21:13.880 --> 21:14.890
Just let me do it.

21:25.550 --> 21:26.570
By the fox's call,

21:27.480 --> 21:28.540
wrathful sandstorm.

21:50.480 --> 21:51.740
Eastern Purple Lightning,

21:53.000 --> 21:54.220
grant me your power.

22:01.200 --> 22:01.780
Ji Ling.

22:02.640 --> 22:03.260
Ji Ling.

23:15.030 --> 23:15.700
Ji Ling.

23:20.510 --> 23:21.090
Ji Ling.

23:22.480 --> 23:23.330
Is that you?

23:25.750 --> 23:26.740
I'm not Ji Ling.

23:27.880 --> 23:29.570
I'm the demon in him.

23:31.480 --> 23:32.300
A Lonescale.

23:35.750 --> 23:37.260
You should be very familiar

23:39.270 --> 23:40.500
with my scent.

23:44.720 --> 23:45.610
The fragrance.

23:47.400 --> 23:48.170
So it's you.

23:51.350 --> 23:52.850
Are you upset?

23:56.480 --> 23:57.020
Yes.

23:58.640 --> 24:00.090
Do you regret it?

24:00.960 --> 24:02.890
Do you want to start over?

24:04.310 --> 24:04.940
Yes.

24:07.720 --> 24:09.300
I have the ability

24:10.550 --> 24:12.060
to rewind time.

24:13.030 --> 24:15.020
I can take you back in time

24:15.920 --> 24:16.980
to change everything.

24:21.350 --> 24:22.650
Go back in time?

24:25.240 --> 24:26.810
Why do you have this power?

24:28.310 --> 24:29.460
Ji Ling

24:31.590 --> 24:33.130
lived his entire life in remorse.

24:34.000 --> 24:36.090
He had always wanted to go back in time

24:37.270 --> 24:38.540
to change everything.

24:40.680 --> 24:42.020
If I hadn't

24:43.720 --> 24:45.370
run out of sacred power,

24:47.720 --> 24:50.170
I could have saved Yuan Wuhuo's brother.

24:53.070 --> 24:54.850
If I can go back in time

24:56.960 --> 24:58.060
and choose again,

25:02.680 --> 25:04.700
will I still swallow that dragon scale?

25:13.000 --> 25:14.650
Is it snowing in South Mountain now?

25:18.070 --> 25:19.020
In the next life,

25:21.070 --> 25:22.980
be a carefree

25:23.000 --> 25:24.260
blind fox.

25:26.720 --> 25:27.500
It's summer.

25:30.240 --> 25:32.060
There must be plenty of raspberries

25:35.440 --> 25:36.780
by the Yumian Lake now.

25:40.480 --> 25:41.740
All his remorse

25:42.550 --> 25:44.090
turned into an obsession

25:46.070 --> 25:47.810
and was absorbed by the dragon scale.

25:48.440 --> 25:49.890
That's how I came into being.

25:51.310 --> 25:53.020
His hundred years of obsession

25:53.640 --> 25:55.610
gave me the ability to go back in time.

25:57.720 --> 25:59.220
Do you wish to go back in time

26:00.830 --> 26:02.700
to save your beloved one?

26:03.480 --> 26:04.170
Yes, I do.

26:10.720 --> 26:12.740
But I have Jiu Ying fragments in me.

26:15.400 --> 26:16.740
He'll notice it.

26:17.830 --> 26:19.780
The world of rewinds I create

26:21.640 --> 26:23.000
is a closed universe

26:23.000 --> 26:24.410
free from the laws

26:24.440 --> 26:25.540
of the outside world.

26:27.270 --> 26:28.780
Jiu Ying can't monitor you.

26:29.480 --> 26:31.740
You can do whatever you want

26:32.640 --> 26:34.220
without any fear of failure.

26:35.240 --> 26:37.060
You can do it over and over again

26:39.110 --> 26:39.780
as long as...

26:42.440 --> 26:43.300
As long as what?

26:44.680 --> 26:45.940
As long as your physical form

26:46.160 --> 26:47.300
can withstand it.

26:48.720 --> 26:49.780
Each rewind

26:50.510 --> 26:52.650
rewrites the past

26:53.240 --> 26:55.460
