37:48.230 --> 37:49.980
and won't be able to sacrifice himself.

37:51.670 --> 37:52.170
No.

37:55.030 --> 37:56.420
I've tried it.

38:09.480 --> 38:10.170
Why?

38:10.420 --> 38:13.000
[Twenty-sixth rewind]

38:13.000 --> 38:14.340
Why doesn't it work?

38:17.000 --> 38:18.380
Taking the ring alone

38:19.150 --> 38:20.940
doesn't change Ji Ling's fate.

38:21.960 --> 38:23.340
I must relieve this drought

38:24.630 --> 38:26.130
with the Dragon Deity's Power.

38:27.760 --> 38:28.250
No.

38:29.480 --> 38:30.020
No.

38:32.280 --> 38:33.020
Why not?

38:34.070 --> 38:35.460
Once the drought is relieved,

38:36.000 --> 38:37.820
The Dragon Deity's Power will dissipate.

38:38.190 --> 38:39.460
It will dissipate?

38:41.000 --> 38:41.900
The Dragon Deity's Power

38:42.630 --> 38:43.940
breaks through all the barriers

38:43.960 --> 38:44.980
and removes all spells.

38:45.550 --> 38:47.380
Didn't Xiaowei lift the Fox-Allure Spell

38:47.480 --> 38:48.250
for the people of Luo'an

38:48.280 --> 38:49.650
with the Dragon Deity's Power?

38:51.760 --> 38:53.210
Lu Wuyi doesn't just want to

38:54.000 --> 38:55.060
relieve the drought.

38:56.070 --> 38:57.380
She also wants to save Ji Ling.

38:59.590 --> 39:00.540
The drought in Luo'an

39:00.630 --> 39:01.290
is destined

39:01.360 --> 39:02.980
to be resolved with Ji Ling's sacrifice.

39:04.440 --> 39:06.020
No matter how many rewinds she attempts,

39:06.800 --> 39:07.650
she can't change

39:07.670 --> 39:09.090
the long-written ending.

39:09.960 --> 39:10.880
If she forcibly

39:10.880 --> 39:12.730
relieves the drought with the Dragon Deity's Power,

39:13.920 --> 39:14.650
she'd be intervening

39:14.670 --> 39:15.920
with Ji Ling's destiny

39:15.920 --> 39:16.860
against the will of heaven.

39:18.280 --> 39:19.170
The Dragon Deity's Power

39:20.400 --> 39:21.860
will naturally dissipate.

39:23.480 --> 39:25.210
Then our long-standing plan...

39:26.480 --> 39:27.060
Wu.

39:29.000 --> 39:29.540
No.

39:29.920 --> 39:30.460
Don't.

39:30.960 --> 39:31.540
Wuyi.

39:32.110 --> 39:32.690
Don't.

39:33.920 --> 39:34.540
Don't.

39:38.880 --> 39:39.690
I insist.

39:42.630 --> 39:43.170
Xiaowei.

39:43.760 --> 39:44.800
Ms. Yu is too badly injured.

39:44.800 --> 39:45.820
She's beyond saving.

39:46.400 --> 39:47.840
You will defy the will of heaven

39:47.840 --> 39:48.540
if you save her

39:48.550 --> 39:49.460
with the Dragon Deity's Power.

39:50.070 --> 39:51.420
You will be reduced to nothing.

39:51.880 --> 39:52.940
I insist.

39:55.360 --> 39:56.730
Even if you resent me,

39:57.920 --> 39:59.650
and even if I'm reduced to nothing,

40:01.190 --> 40:02.420
I want you alive.

40:06.000 --> 40:07.020
I won't let you die.

40:27.550 --> 40:29.290
I have seen through your moves

40:29.840 --> 40:31.420
in my countless rewinds.

40:31.960 --> 40:33.290
Your spells can't contain me.

40:34.630 --> 40:36.420
My sacred power has surpassed yours.

40:37.760 --> 40:38.980
You can't stop me.

40:54.320 --> 40:55.540
I have no sacred power.

40:57.230 --> 40:58.860
You have my ring.

41:02.590 --> 41:04.380
But I must stop you.

41:07.920 --> 41:08.650
Wu.

41:11.670 --> 41:13.060
Don't do this for me.

41:15.400 --> 41:16.130
It's not worth it.

41:18.590 --> 41:19.420
Ji Ling.

41:21.510 --> 41:22.610
Let go.

41:42.150 --> 41:42.860
Wuyi.

41:43.550 --> 41:44.690
Dreamfall.

42:07.440 --> 42:08.610
Thank you

42:09.320 --> 42:10.820
for getting rid of them for me.

42:19.920 --> 42:21.650
Hand over the Dragon Deity's Power of Han Ba,

42:22.630 --> 42:23.420
and I will spare you.

42:25.800 --> 42:26.900
Yuan Wuhuo.

42:45.190 --> 42:46.210
You've been hiding for ages.

42:48.110 --> 42:48.900
Finally, you can't help

42:48.920 --> 42:50.020
but show up.

42:51.320 --> 42:52.770
Since you knew it was me,

42:53.630 --> 42:54.770
