42:56.630 --> 42:57.500
You know

42:59.320 --> 43:01.610
what people become after they go through

43:03.110 --> 43:04.340
dozens of rewinds?

43:07.150 --> 43:07.770
What?

43:09.760 --> 43:10.820
They become deities.

43:20.400 --> 43:21.420
They know

43:22.360 --> 43:23.420
